Child dreams become true
The kindergartens and nurseries in the Zollernalbkreis get postal service in these days.
That Black Forest messenger would like to support the arrangements in collaboration with building house and the savings bank Zollernalb in the realization of its building wishes and improvement wishes.
Does the kindergarten need a new sand box?
All kindergartens, nurseries and child manger can joining in in the action out of the entire Zollernalbkreis.
If you have a building wish or improvement wish for your arrangement, you can apply yourself with this in that Black Forest messengers.
Be creative with your children and surprise the jury of the action kindergarten construction site.
A jury, consisting of representatives of Black Forest messenger, building house and savings bank Zollernalb, selects out of all contributions three wishes from.
Which prerequisites does to the participation it give?
The wish should be, to realize with building material in the value of maximally 2000 Euro and at a (action) day.
In addition the winner himself must provide for many diligent building helpers.
What does it have with the action day and the helpers on itself?
Building house makes available Zollernalb with support of the savings bank the material.
It is delivered at the arranged day into the kindergarten and should process become then directly by the helpers.
Helpers can parents, grandparents, friends, societies and natural the educators and children themselves be.
